Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine

The Flow Engine main classes, the Flow Engine Compiler and the Flow Engine Configuration classes.

See: Description

    Interface for providing support to resolve a schema URI into an XType.

    Class Description

    Class that locates and creates blocks based on their name.

    The Advance Data Flow Engine main program.

    A type functions class to work with regular Java types.

    AdvancePluginManager.AdvancePluginDetails<T,X,C>

    AdvanceTypeFunctions
    The type functions for the AdvanceType type system.
    AdvanceXTypeFunctions
    A type functions class to work with regular Java types.
